            <td class="blob-code">}</td>
            </tr>

        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
</p>
<p>These are collectively called Magic Methods.</p>
<h2 id="the-magic-get">The Magic __get() <a class="headerlink" href="magic-methods#the-magic-get" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>There are actually just a few magic methods: let's look at another common one.
In <code>battle.php</code>, scroll down a little bit to where it shows the ship health. Change
this: instead of <code>$ship1-&gt;getStrength()</code>, say <code>$ship1-&gt;strength</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="fb51d143c4">
    <div class="meta">
